{"type":"message","id":"10368bfb","parentId":"f85ad833","timestamp":"2026-04-04T06:08:20.680Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Refining Connection Retry Logic**\n\nI've just finished the requested optimizations for `ECBackgroundManager.m`. Specifically, I refactored the reconnection logic to include an exponential backoff strategy, which tracks failed attempts with `_reconnectRetryCount`. The fixed 10-second delay has been replaced with one that scales, improving resilience.\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_afeddee55c393790","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep \"scheduleReconnectWithDelay\" /Volumes/MACOS/my/ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager.m"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":30377,"output":41,"cacheRead":8174,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38592,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775282896357,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4ce924f2-6139-4d25-80c7-430943c0a5da"}}
