{"type":"message","id":"54bcacce","parentId":"289bba74","timestamp":"2026-04-04T06:08:28.376Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Confirming Replacements and Optimization**\n\nI've confirmed that all instances of `_scheduleReconnectWithDelay:` have been successfully replaced, as the `grep` command yielded no results. Additionally, I've optimized the `ECBackgroundManager.m` file as specified.\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我已完成对 `/Volumes/MACOS/my/ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager.m` 的代码优化，针对 WebSocket 重连机制进行了重构。\n\n### 主要改动说明：\n\n1.  **引入指数退避算法 (Exponential Backoff)**：\n    *   新增 `_reconnectRetryCount` 变量记录失败次数。\n    *   重连间隔计算公式改为：`delay = min(2^retryCount, 30.0)`。重连时间随失败次数倍增（2s, 4s, 8s, 16s...），最大上限为 30 秒。这能有效防止由于网络波动导致的密集无效连接请求，降低 CPU 占用并提高应用在后台的存活率。\n\n2.  **严谨的状态管理 (Timer 清理)**：\n    *   将 `dispatch_after` 逻辑替换为 `NSTimer` 驱动。\n    *   新增 `_stopReconnectTimer` 方法。在每次计划重连前及 WebSocket 连接建立成功时，都会主动清理旧的 Timer。此举确保了同一时间只有一个重连任务，避免了因竞态条件产生的多个重连循环。\n    *   连接成功后自动重置 `_reconnectRetryCount`。\n\n3.  **日志记录增强**：\n    *   在计划重连、定时器触发及连接成功等关键节点增加了详细的日志（通过 `ECLogManager`），日志中包含当前的尝试次数和延迟时长。\n\n### 代码修改片段：\n\n```objectivec\n// [v2026] 重连管理\nNSInteger _reconnectRetryCount;\nNSTimer *_reconnectTimer;\n\n// ...\n\n// 安排重连（引入指数退避算法：2, 4, 8, 16... 最高 30s）\n- (void)_scheduleReconnect {\n  [self _stopReconnectTimer]; // 严谨清理旧 Timer，防止竞态\n\n  _reconnectRetryCount++;\n  NSTimeInterval delay = pow(2, _reconnectRetryCount);\n  if (delay > 30.0) {\n    delay = 30.0;\n  }\n\n  dispatch_async(dispatch_get_main_queue(), ^{\n    [[ECLogManager sharedManager]\n        log:[NSString stringWithFormat:@\"[Tunnel] ⚠️ 连接异常，准备第 %ld 次重连，将在 %.0f 秒后进行...\",\n                                       (long)self->_reconnectRetryCount, delay]];\n\n    self->_reconnectTimer = [NSTimer\n        scheduledTimerWithTimeInterval:delay\n                               repeats:NO\n                                 block:^(NSTimer *_Nonnull timer) {\n                                   NSLog(@\"[Tunnel] 🔄 重连定时器触发，开始尝试连接...\");\n                                   [self startTunnel];\n                                 }];\n  });\n}\n\n// ...\n\n- (void)URLSession:(NSURLSession *)session\n          webSocketTask:(NSURLSessionWebSocketTask *)webSocketTask\n    didOpenWithProtocol:(NSString *)protocol {\n  @synchronized(self) {\n    // ...\n    self->_reconnectRetryCount = 0; // 连接成功，重置计数\n  }\n  [self _stopReconnectTimer]; // 连接成功，确保停止重连定时\n  // ...\n}\n```\n\n修改已成功保存至文件。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":23791,"output":734,"cacheRead":8168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32693,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775282900730,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ffb7d05f-d14a-4ab0-b3ff-6cc9b2e6b708"}}
